      "writtenOn": "2018-02-14T07:13:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, I agree with this idea. I will revert this CL and just change only these expected values.\n\n\nJust to be clear, I think the number range must be 37 ~ 38.\nLet\u0027s assume that the correct value in CSS is 38 + a, where 0 \u003c\u003d a \u003c 1.\n\nfloor((38 + a) * scale) / scale \u003c\u003d (38 + a) * scale / scale\n-\u003e floor( floor((38 + a) * scale) / scale ) \u003c\u003d floor( (38 + a) * scale / scale ) \u003d\u003d 38\n\nfloor((38 + a) * scale) / scale \u003e (38 + a) * scale / scale - 1\n-\u003e floor( floor((38 + a) * scale) / scale ) \u003e\u003d floor( (38 + a) * scale / scale - 1 ) \u003d\u003d 37",
